The total associated area is 94.93 m2, which consists of : entrance hallway / 6.82 m2 / with a built-in wardrobe measuring 3 meters, making storage in the apartment hassle-free, southeast-facing living room with kitchen / up to 25.56 m2 /, offering views of the Little Fatra and Martinky, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The living room is connected to the kitchen, aesthetically separated by a feature ceiling that also houses the lighting fixtures, t has access to a balcony that runs the entire width of the living room, the bedroom (18.9 m2) is furnished with a double bed, nightstands, and wardrobes, and boasts an ideal location that new owners will appreciate, especially in the summer months, as it is north-facing, preventing overheating and eliminating the need for a heating system. Additionally, there are two bathrooms, one of which has a separate shower room and another with a toilet. The apartment also features a large balcony overlooking the cityscape and a private parking space in the underground garage. The price of the property is 292000 € . Monthly management fees for the apartment: 215 € / month including security services. Parking: private parking space in the underground garage is not included in the price. The price of the premium parking space, where you can park both a car and a trailer or motorcycle, is available for an additional fee (the owner is currently preparing for an electric charging station)."}
